{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce regulation for infant care and sleep advice providers",
        "additional_details": "Introduce regulation for infant care and sleep advice providers, including mandatory standards for training courses and qualifications.\r\nThis should include:\r\nRegulation and quality assurance of training courses and certification pathways\r\nRecognised minimum qualification requirements\r\nSupervised practical experience before working with clients independently\r\nA requirement to follow evidence-based guidance aligned with NHS and public health recommendations\r\nOversight by an appropriate body",
        "background": "We want the government to ensure individuals who work in the parenting space, advising on the health and wellbeing of infants, toddlers, children and families to be tightly regulated to prevent harm.",
